 yes, you can use a stream cipher chip to hash data with only slight 
 modification. see:
 
 `a fast cryptographic checksum algorithm based on stream ciphers', x lai,
 ra rueppel, j woolven, auscrypt 92 pp 8-7 to 8-11.
 
